    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The exterior shows heavy signs of age, including noticeable rust spots on the wheel arches, several large dents on the passenger side, and a fading clear coat. Inside, the upholstery is torn in multiple places and the electronics are inconsistent. Mechanically, the engine runs but has a persistent leak and the transmission shifts roughly. This is an ideal project for someone looking for a restoration challenge or a source for parts. Sold strictly as-is.",
